==León===
*1524 León founded by Spain 
*[[21 August]] [[1685]] - [[14 September]] [[1685]] León captured by pirates under Dampier. 
*[[15 September]] [[1821]] Declaration of independence from Spain of the Kingdom of Guatemala (encompassing all present Central America plus Chiapas). 
*[[28 September]] [[1821]] León, while awaiting developments with regard to Spain, declares separation from the Kingdom of Guatemala (Acta de Nublados). 
*[[12 October]] [[1821]] Incorporated into Mexico (de jure situation ambiguous [ratified [[5 January]] [[1822]]]). 
*[[17 April]] [[1823]] León declares itself an "orphan" and thus sovereign. 
*[[1 July]] [[1823]] The Central American Federation (see under Guatemala) proclaims independence from Mexico and invites those provinces that had left the Kingdom of Guatemala to join. 
*[[2 July]] [[1823]] León accedes to invitation; incorporation into Central America. 
*[[4 January]] [[1825]] León surrenders to the authority of Manuel Arzú, commissioned by the federal government. 

